                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/courses" class="button">Explore More Courses</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>We're proud of your achievement and look forward to supporting you in your continued learning journey!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
